{
  "stem": "9558.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have to use that for the whole families, because at that time Wisnicz was judenrein.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took everybody away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was an ordinary-- [DRINKS] was an ordinary Gentile.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nice guy.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was this chief of the police.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a very, very nice man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He helped so many people, and--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He did something for the Polish government in 1936 or '37.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when the communists came to power, the first thing they-- they remembered what he was doing at that time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the guy risked his life through the war helping people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Such a nice person he was-- while we were in Wisnicz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We still had a [NON-ENGLISH] and used to slaughter, you know, for kosher meat and everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when they went to the police in town, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he went there, so he used to send his son or his daughter on the bicycle and tell him clean up the room, you know, wash up all the blood, you know.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nobody should see it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was real.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A real mensch.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And then the Russian came, and they took him away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was the end of him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After the war, I was told.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't-- I really don't remember exactly--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--because I never went back there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I knew about it, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The brought her into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was the last time I saw her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SOBBING] [DRINKS]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's not easy for me to live all those years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] Why did I survive?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Out of nine children?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 15 SECONDS] And then you were taken to Szebnie.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have a guilty conscience.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SOBBING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember the trip, but--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was it-- it was more frightful than the trip from Bochnia.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
